      "It’s not what you’d call “good” but at least interesting.  Not fully a slasher as it’s more of an anthology movie, but one segment is basically a slasher short film.  The other two are in other subgenres, the second being a kind of revenge/murder plot and the third being more in the satanic/religious vein.  The wraparound is basically a train, I guess to the afterlife?  Anyway, God and the devil (two men in suits) are sitting at a table discussing and arguing about the fates of certain people and that’s how the stories come up.  Anyway, the second segment was the best for me with the “death club”.. otherwise, it was pretty much a mediocre anthology.",
