      "This is one of those “murder by proxy” type movies where someone uses the product of their experiments to do the actual killing.  It’s not so much of a supernatural/monster movie as it is pseudo-scientific creation of a ghoul that just is living but sometimes goes into “ghoul mode” needs to feed on hearts to survive.  And at the very end is a message that buying war bonds is not giving money away, just lending money, and that bonds are available “here”, wherever “here” is.",
